Description

Do you remember World of Mario ? Thi is a journey of super boy.

In heat jungle, Mario must pass so much threats to run to target world. On his road,
You are the first person gaming experience emotional and exciting. You will enjoy adventures full of danger with Mario. Game has a lot of traps, monsters, and unexpected situations through each level that we have built.
In heat jungle, Mario must pass so much threats to run to target world. The boy Mario can jump, run and Mario can use weapon to kill monster but weapon is hidden in somewhere on the jungle to kill all enemies on the way.
+ Use button to jump, move and fire
+ Find weapon in flowers

We hope you enjoy the free game.
Have fun!! :)

Features

• Wonderful high-resolution graphics
• Easy, intuitive controls
• 10 levels

+ So much scenes (jungle, frozen, cave, subway world ….)
+ Addictive gameplay
